sources.description:
A recently released parolee reunites with his old crew, hell-bent on recovering a buried bag of cash stolen from a botched DEA bust five years ago. But a retired sheriff, driven by an unrelenting obsession to correct past mistakes, is hot on their trail. In the heart of the desert, their paths collide in a relentless, gun-blazing showdown where only one side will walk away.
2020.  Stars: Luke Goss, Val Kilmer, Mike Hatton
